13 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
14 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 68 O.S. 2021, Section 3604, as
15 last amended by Section 157, Chapter 452, O.S.L. 2024 (68 O.S. Supp.
16 2025, Section 3604), is amended to read as follows:
17 Section 3604. A. Except as otherwise provided in subsection I
18 or subsection L of this section, an establishment which meets the
19 qualifications specified in the Oklahoma Quality Jobs Program Act
