21 the Oklahoma Tax Commission pursuant to the provisions of the
22 Oklahoma Quality Jobs Program Act; provided, such an establishment
23 defined or classified in the NAICS North American Industry
24 Classification System (NAICS) Manual under U.S. Industry No. 711211
